text: The 1942 Tennessee gubernatorial election was held on November 3, 1942. Incumbent Democrat Prentice Cooper defeated Republican nominee C. N. Frazier with 70.15% of the vote. ==Primary elections== Primary elections were held on August 6, 1942. ===Democratic primary=== ====Candidates==== *Prentice Cooper, incumbent Governor *John Ridley Mitchell, former U.S. Representative *J. Bailey Wray ====Results==== ==General election== ===Candidates=== *Prentice Cooper, Democratic *C. N. Frazier, Republican ===Results=== ==References== 1942 Tennessee Gubernatorial
title: 1942 Tennessee gubernatorial election
